				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">BoC.....-does- it work for us?<a name="46680"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 17 04 2:04 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I recently started playing around with one of these...and needless to say I'm rather sadly disappointed with the results.
<br />

<br />
I have Weapon Affinity 5, so the proc goes off reasonably often.  It just doesn't seem to do anything, just like all other procs.  Even when I engaged a mob first, a monk(which has no form of taunt other than melee) still out-agro'd multiple times even FDing it off.  This is with BoC in main hand.
<br />

<br />
It would not surprise me if SoE made it so BoC simply did not work for bards, just to make sure we are never able to have a way of holding agro <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-12.gif" border="0" alt="Mad" hspace="2" /> 
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
