				<td colspan="2"><span>note - lots of assumptions in here
<br />

<br />
From my use of one it does indead work for us but it is not the aggro that it once was. eb is 700 aggro and with WA5 you should see on average 3 ppm or 2100 aggro per minute . Using the assumption that 1 pt aggro is equal to 1 pt of possible damage you are generating about (assume 60 dps with that weapon) around 6000 aggro per minute (no songs). a nominal 200 dps monk is probably closer to 12000 aggro per minute. So if you want to get aggro you are going to need to add your chants or shield song and he will need to control his aggro.
<br />

<br />
Snasty
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
