<br />

<br />
Only issue is when I'm 2 boxing with my cleric, he's squishy, so I try like mad to keep aggro over him. Course he's reverse DSing the mob, healing me, melleeing with his 150 proc DD hammer and 925 pt nuking.  
<br />

<br />
Over the last few days, I've been 2 boxing the VoS camp, and I must say, with slow, WoZ, Riz and PoV, and my 120 proc DD sword, I hold aggro over just about everything at that camp up until the second Cheal. Then I just mez the mob, back the cleric off, reslow and solo it for a bit, the move the cleric back in.  Heck he's got about 3k hp, sometimes I let him tank if we're below 20% health on the mob.
<br />

<br />
Good to read the reasons for our lack of aggro... but I have a better reason... we're so charismatic and suave that impossible to NOT like a bard.  You wouldn't hit someone you liked, even if you are a dragon or whathaveyou. hehe
<br />

